gamma characteristics.

00:08:01.930 --> 00:08:05.290 align:middle line:84%
But this range extended far
beyond the gamma waves that

00:08:05.290 --> 00:08:06.740 align:middle line:90%
had been measured in the past.

00:08:06.740 --> 00:08:07.540 align:middle line:90%
Listen to this.

00:08:07.540 --> 00:08:12.550 align:middle line:10%
It went from 44 hertz
all the way to 100 hertz.

00:08:12.550 --> 00:08:17.810 align:middle line:10%
Look at the range of this state,
44 to 100 cycles per second.

00:08:17.810 --> 00:08:20.710 align:middle line:84%
But it had the same
characteristics as gamma.

00:08:20.710 --> 00:08:24.110 align:middle line:84%
So it was a higher
form of gamma.

00:08:24.110 --> 00:08:25.780 align:middle line:84%
So this newly-discovered
brain state

00:08:25.780 --> 00:08:28.660 align:middle line:90%
