of the brain's capacity.

00:08:42.210 --> 00:08:44.650 align:middle line:90%
There must not be anything else.

00:08:44.650 --> 00:08:48.990 align:middle line:84%
And when they felt
that, further research

00:08:48.990 --> 00:08:53.280 align:middle line:84%
revealed yet another,
even higher brain state.

00:08:53.280 --> 00:08:56.730 align:middle line:84%
And this, again, was revealed
through the meditation,

00:08:56.730 --> 00:08:58.770 align:middle line:90%
