the brain becomes synchronized.

00:09:36.870 --> 00:09:41.490 align:middle line:84%
And in that synchronization,
it allows tremendous levels,

00:09:41.490 --> 00:09:45.090 align:middle line:84%
tremendous states
of self-regulation.

